image_analysis.description: A photograph of a narrow interior hallway. The walls are painted a light cream or beige color. On the right wall, there is a large piece of modern art depicting a figure in yellow and black tones. At the end of the hallway, there is a white double-door closet. Two circular flush-mount ceiling lights are visible. On the left floor, there is a red fire extinguisher. Red tape or a protective strip runs along the baseboards on both sides of the floor. A light switch or small panel is visible on the center wall segment.
image_analysis.layout: Interior architectural view looking down a corridor.
